character.name:
pixel art RPG character,
front view idle sprite,
same proportions and style as a simple RPG archer character,

a light blue mage:
wearing simple blue clothes,
short tunic or robe (very simple),
dark blue pants,
brown boots,

short staff or wand,
no cape,
no long flowing clothes,
no complex accessories,

clear readable silhouette,
simple colors,
clean pixel art,
fits perfectly in a classic isometric RPG
